<section class="brand--hm-treasury brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What UK Financial Investments Limited does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>UK Financial Investments Limited (UKFI) manages the government’s investments in the Royal Bank of Scotland (RBS), Lloyds Banking Group (Lloyds) and UK Asset Resolution Ltd (UKAR). UKFI is a company with HM Treasury as its sole shareholder and operates at arm’s length from government.</p>

<p><abbr title="UK Financial Investments Limited">UKFI</abbr> works with <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/hm-treasury">HM Treasury</a> and the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/uk-government-investments">UK Government Investments</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/uk-financial-investments-limited/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



